and looks like a devil.

574
00:29:00,640 --> 00:29:01,680
Rangrang, look at that fish.

575
00:29:01,760 --> 00:29:03,200
It's so pretty and cute.

576
00:29:03,280 --> 00:29:05,680
Children, we should learn
from this young lady

577
00:29:05,760 --> 00:29:06,840
and love marine life.

578
00:29:07,640 --> 00:29:09,520
It's getting more attractive.

579
00:29:09,600 --> 00:29:11,080
It's so fleshy.

580
00:29:11,160 --> 00:29:13,000
It would be delicious
as Sichuan boiled fish.

581
00:29:13,080 --> 00:29:14,520
The size is just right.

582
00:29:14,600 --> 00:29:16,000
My pot at home is exactly this big.

583
00:29:17,840 --> 00:29:20,200
Miss, this young lady wants to eat it!

584
00:29:20,280 --> 00:29:22,040
Don't!

585
00:29:22,120 --> 00:29:24,400
I don't plan to eat it right now.

586
00:29:24,480 --> 00:29:26,200
She's joking with you. She can't eat it.

587
00:29:26,280 --> 00:29:27,240
She can't eat it.

588
00:29:28,640 --> 00:29:30,200
The young lady won't actually eat it.

589
00:29:30,280 --> 00:29:31,960
She said that because she finds it cute

590
00:29:32,040 --> 00:29:34,080
{\an8}and really likes it.

591
00:29:35,280 --> 00:29:36,360
Really?

592
00:29:38,080 --> 00:29:39,600
You're very cute too.

593
00:29:47,880 --> 00:29:48,880
Rangrang,

594
00:29:48,960 --> 00:29:51,680
I didn't know
you were so good at coaxing kids.

595
00:29:52,840 --> 00:29:53,760
I'm not.

596
00:29:55,000 --> 00:29:55,960
I was forced to.

597
00:29:57,880 --> 00:29:59,200
Well,

598
00:29:59,280 --> 00:30:02,080
can you coax a 200-month-old kid?

599
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:08,640
You don't have to.

600
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:11,000
Kids who are 200 months old are sensible.

601
00:30:30,960 --> 00:30:31,800
<i>Rangrang!</i>

602
00:30:40,840 --> 00:30:41,840
<i>Su Zaizai.</i>

603
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:55,680
<i>Hello.</i>

604
00:30:55,760 --> 00:30:57,560
<i>We're currently rehearsing our lines.</i>

605
00:30:57,640 --> 00:30:59,400
<i>Beside me is my male lead,</i>

606
00:30:59,480 --> 00:31:00,840
<i>Prince Rangrang.</i>

607
00:31:03,040 --> 00:31:04,280
<i>Su Zaizai,</i>

608
00:31:04,360 --> 00:31:06,440
<i>have you memorized
the final paragraph of your lines?</i>

609
00:31:08,880 --> 00:31:10,840
<i>I used to think</i>

610
00:31:10,920 --> 00:31:12,160
<i>that it was the fairy's magic</i>

611
00:31:12,240 --> 00:31:14,240
<i>that turned me into a princess.</i>

612
00:31:14,320 --> 00:31:17,080
<i>It wasn't until the clock struck midnight</i>

613
00:31:17,160 --> 00:31:19,320
<i>that I was brought back to reality.</i>

614
00:31:19,840 --> 00:31:22,560
<i>How can I be good enough for you?</i>

615
00:31:26,680 --> 00:31:27,840
<i>Have you forgotten your lines?</i>

616
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:30,240
<i>Rangrang,</i>

617
00:31:30,320 --> 00:31:31,840
<i>I think I've found the reason</i>

618
00:31:31,920 --> 00:31:33,320
<i>I always get stuck here.</i>

619
00:31:34,080 --> 00:31:35,200
<i>What is it?</i>

620
00:31:35,280 --> 00:31:37,520
<i>It's because I can't accept it.</i>

621
00:31:37,600 --> 00:31:38,480
<i>I think</i>

622
00:31:38,560 --> 00:31:40,120
<i>Cinderella thinks too little of herself.</i>

623
00:31:40,200 --> 00:31:42,280
<i>Why isn't she</i><i>good enough for the prince?</i>

624
00:31:42,360 --> 00:31:44,520
<i>Does only a princess deserve a prince?</i>

625
00:31:44,600 --> 00:31:45,680
<i>I don't think so.</i>

626
00:31:46,440 --> 00:31:48,120
<i>I want to ask Mr. Xiao
to change the script.</i>

627
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:50,040
<i>Rangrang, how should we change it?</i>

628
00:31:55,360 --> 00:31:56,840
<i>Maybe we can change it to this.</i>

629
00:31:58,480 --> 00:32:00,240
<i>Perhaps every girl</i>

630
00:32:00,320 --> 00:32:01,880
<i>can become a princess</i>

631
00:32:02,600 --> 00:32:04,040
<i>in front of the one that she loves.</i>

632
00:32:07,520 --> 00:32:10,320
<i>Sixteen-year-old girls seem to be able</i>

633
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:11,720
<i>to constantly immerse themselves</i>

634
00:32:11,800 --> 00:32:13,040
<i>in novels and movies,</i>

635
00:32:13,120 --> 00:32:15,840
<i>making it their sweet and lovely secret.</i>
